        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite: Proficiency in &amp;reference[Stealth]</strong> </em></p><p><em>You coordinate your allies, allowing them to follow your lead and stay out of sight.</em></p><p><strong>Reaction</strong> - 1 Creature (90 ft.)</p><ul><li><p>After an ally other than yourself rolls a stealth check, you can roll a [[/check skill=stealth]]{stealth check} yourself to replace their roll, potentially allowing them to be undetected. A character can also not be affected by this feature more than once on a given roll.</p></li></ul>",
